(106, 1, '2017-05-27 20:49:59', '2017-05-27 20:49:59', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>On A Smart Phone</h2>\r\n<span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/www.thegivebackcampaign.png" /></span>\r\n<div class="td_txt-color">\r\n\r\nIf you\'ve a smartphone you can use it to search, track and support causes close to your heart.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/cms_images/328386482085929.png" alt="The Give Back Campaign App" width="150" height="85" border="0" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nDownload the app from the app store by typing The Give Back Campaign into the itunes search engine. <a class="cs_cmp_link" href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Or click on this link</a>, or by visiting the Android Play Store via this <a class="cs_cmp_link" title="" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thegivebackcampaign.gbc" target="blank">link</a>\r\n\r\nHow to use our Smartphone App\r\n\r\nOpen the app and you\'ll see the following screen\r\n\r\n<span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/GBCiphonesml.png" /></span>\r\n\r\nHere you can\r\n\r\nSearch Business - Search For All Businesses\r\nSearch Local Business - Within a 5km Radius of your current position\r\nFundraising Campaigns - Search for Campaigns from all our Organisations\r\nHot Deals - View All Retailer Hot Deals\r\nNews - Read our latest news\r\nHelp - How to use the App\r\nLogin (Top Right) - Access Your Account\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Trigger Donations</strong> - Most Important Feature\r\n\r\nTriggering donations to your favourite cause is as simple as giving your mobile number to any shop assistant of a participating business at the time of paying your bill.\r\n\r\nIt\'s that simple.\r\n\r\nStart shopping with retail partners and see just how easy it is.\r\n\r\nYou don\'t need to do anything with the app to trigger a donation, the app just lets you view businesses, track campaigns, support them, keep up to date with our latest news and see your account details\r\n<div><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thegivebackcampaign.gbc" target="blank"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com//images/siteimages/googleplay.jpg" alt="Available in the Google Play Store" border="0" /></span></a><a href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8" target="blank"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com//images/siteimages/appstoresm.jpg" alt="Available in the App Store" border="0" /></span></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'On a Smart Phone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-27 20:49:59', '2017-05-27 20:49:59', '', 17, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(107, 1, '2017-05-27 20:50:32', '2017-05-27 20:50:32', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2><span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/www.thegivebackcampaign.png" /></span></h2>\r\n<div class="td_txt-color">\r\n\r\nIf you\'ve a smartphone you can use it to search, track and support causes close to your heart.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/cms_images/328386482085929.png" alt="The Give Back Campaign App" width="150" height="85" border="0" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nDownload the app from the app store by typing The Give Back Campaign into the itunes search engine. <a class="cs_cmp_link" href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Or click on this link</a>, or by visiting the Android Play Store via this <a class="cs_cmp_link" title="" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thegivebackcampaign.gbc" target="blank">link</a>\r\n\r\nHow to use our Smartphone App\r\n\r\nOpen the app and you\'ll see the following screen\r\n\r\n<span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/GBCiphonesml.png" /></span>\r\n\r\nHere you can\r\n\r\nSearch Business - Search For All Businesses\r\nSearch Local Business - Within a 5km Radius of your current position\r\nFundraising Campaigns - Search for Campaigns from all our Organisations\r\nHot Deals - View All Retailer Hot Deals\r\nNews - Read our latest news\r\nHelp - How to use the App\r\nLogin (Top Right) - Access Your Account\r\n\r\n<strong>How to Trigger Donations</strong> - Most Important Feature\r\n\r\nTriggering donations to your favourite cause is as simple as giving your mobile number to any shop assistant of a participating business at the time of paying your bill.\r\n\r\nIt\'s that simple.\r\n\r\nStart shopping with retail partners and see just how easy it is.\r\n\r\nYou don\'t need to do anything with the app to trigger a donation, the app just lets you view businesses, track campaigns, support them, keep up to date with our latest news and see your account details\r\n<div><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thegivebackcampaign.gbc" target="blank"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com//images/siteimages/googleplay.jpg" alt="Available in the Google Play Store" border="0" /></span></a><a href="http://itunes.apple.com/au/app/the-give-back-campaign/id540971702?mt=8" target="blank"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://thegivebackcampaign.com//images/siteimages/appstoresm.jpg" alt="Available in the App Store" border="0" /></span></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'On a Smart Phone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-27 20:50:32', '2017-05-27 20:50:32', '', 17, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
