(110, 1, '2017-05-27 20:53:19', '2017-05-27 20:53:19', 'We have three different types of participation, Supporter, Organisation / Charity and Business. Click the image below to go through and sign up.\r\n\r\nIf you own a business and you wish to sign up as both, please Register as a Supporter first then you\'ll see a business registration link after you\'ve completed your registration.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/consumer/signup"><span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/supporterrego.png" width="225" height="52" border="0" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nSigning up will allow you to shop and earn your favourite charity a donation with every purchase made with Give Back businesses. Please note that if your favourite organisation is not listed let us know and we will invite them to join The Give Back Campaign and you can then change who you are supporting.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/organisation/signup"><span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/charityrego.png" width="225" height="52" border="0" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nIf your organisation is looking for more funds and a consistent stream of revenue, register your organisation today. Every time your donors spend money you could earn a donation.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/business/signup"><span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/businessrego.png" width="225" height="52" border="0" /></span></a>\r\n\r\nIf you believe in the concept of Giving Back when charity customers shop with you, register your business and see how powerful this program is. Gain access to millins of donors of charities.', 'Sign Up to The Give Back Campaign', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sign-up-to-the-give-back-campaign', '', '', '2017-05-27 20:53:19', '2017-05-27 20:53:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0),
