(119, 1, '2017-05-27 20:59:12', '2017-05-27 20:59:12', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span class="img-border"><img src="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/spread%20the%20word.png" /></span>\r\n<div class="td_txt-color">\r\n\r\nAs part of our drive to recruit as many retailers to our cause we\'re offering you the opportunity to earn your cause <strong><u>$50</u></strong> for every business you refer to us that joins The Giveback Campaign\r\n\r\nDepending upon how many businesses you know, this could provide you with an excellent opportunity to help your charity or yourself.\r\n\r\nThere are tens of thousands of businesses out there who are looking to help their community. Restaurants, hairdressers, cafes, accommodation places, pubs, you name it , they\'re out there.\r\n\r\nIn just a week with our website or through our iphone or android apps you could invite 10 or 20 businesses to join us.\r\n\r\nJust imagine how quickly your cause, club, school , favourite charity or your own account could benefit.\r\n\r\nSo how to get started.\r\n\r\n<strong>Via this Website</strong>\r\nSign into your <a title="" href="http://thegivebackcampaign.com/login" target="">Supporter Account</a> through the link in the top right corner of this page\r\nClick on the My Details link in the left menu and choose to Donate Referral Bonus or Keep Referral Bonus\r\nThen click on the "Spread the Word" link and enter the business owners name and email address and we\'ll send off your invitation\r\n\r\n<strong>Via our Iphone or Android App</strong>\r\nAlternatively Sign into your account through the app and go to the Spread the Word by entering the business owners name and email address. We\'ll send a personalised invitation to the business to Join The Give Back Campaign with you as their referrer.\r\n<table border="0" width="100%">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div align="center"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/smallsupporters.png" /></span></div></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div align="center"><span class="img-border"><img src="http://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/smallspread.png" /></span></div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Spread the Word', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'spread-the-word', '', '', '2017-05-27 20:59:28', '2017-05-27 20:59:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/?page_id=119', 0, 'page', '', 0),
