(128, 1, '2017-05-27 21:03:36', '2017-05-27 21:03:36', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]Are you a pure online business selling products or services?\r\n\r\n<span class="img-border"><img src="http://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/images/siteimages/eb2.jpg" alt="Edible Blooms" border="0" /></span>\r\n\r\nIf you\'re like our friends at Edible Blooms you\'re selling online and may have no retail presence.\r\n\r\nHow can you benefit from being involved with the Give Back Campaign? Simply, here\'s how.\r\n\r\nLike retail businesses you\'re always looking for sales. The Give Back campaign has the ability to track purchases made by our supporters through your website via a number of tracking functions that make increased sales an easily achieved target and helps track the donations applicable to customers charities.\r\n\r\nThrough a partnership with one of the largest e commerce tracking partners, The Give Back campaign can supply you tracking code, validation code and help promote your online portal within hours of you being signed onto the Give Back Campaign program.\r\n\r\nYou\'ll be required to pay the same signup fee plus lodge your credit card with us for all future commissions we earn as donations to charity. This way it means all donations to charity can be met by charging your credit card.\r\n\r\nHow does the Give Back Campaign market you?\r\n\r\nWe include your site in our online directory as well as provide links in our consumer app including your Give Back rate, any specials you may have and web link to your site\r\nWe also promote you in our weekly emails to our members as well as via Facebook and Twitter.\r\nWe also profile a business once a month and your business may be chosen for this promotion.\r\n\r\nIn addition to promoting you to all our consumers, we again notify all our charity partners of the relationship and ask them to promote you on their Facebook and Twitter accounts as well as include you in their member newsletters.\r\n\r\nThe Give Back Campaign may also promote you in our web feed to our charity partner sites if you have seasonal offers and specials.\r\n\r\nThis is an excellent value package and puts you in front of tens of thousands of consumers all looking to make purchases to help their charities.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.buyabale.com.au/the-give-back-campaign" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Have a look here to see how the web feed might look if your business was included</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/business/signup">Register your business online today with the Give Back Campaign </a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Online Businesses', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'online-businesses', '', '', '2017-05-27 21:03:47', '2017-05-27 21:03:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/?page_id=128', 0, 'page', '', 0),
