(141, 1, '2017-05-27 22:09:58', '2017-05-27 22:09:58', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text][soliloquy id="55"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="70" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1495914465319{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="71" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1495914470894{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="72" img_size="full" css=".vc_custom_1495914477837{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class="slogan"><strong>What do we do?</strong> The Give Back Campaign brings together businesses and causes in order for them to help each other. Businesses commit to supporting causes by making a donation every time a supporter makes a purchase. Organisations then commit to supporting businesses by encouraging their supporters to purchase through the business. In a nutshell - the more the supporters support the business, the more the business supports the cause.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n<section id="mobilenone" class="columns" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">\r\n<h2><span class="sss">Fundraising Calculator - How much can your charity / cause raise each week, month, year?</span></h2>\r\nChoose how many supporters you have, how many dollars they might spend each week, what Give Back rate they earn for you and over how many weeks. Press Calculate\r\n\r\n<form id="calcfun_frm" action="https://thegivebackcampaign.com/action/calculator_fund" method="post">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Supporter</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Money Spent</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Giveback %</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Weeks</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td width="250px"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><select name="supportes">\r\n<option value="1">1</option>\r\n<opt