(182, 1, '2017-06-04 19:06:52', '2017-06-04 19:06:52', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<table class="org_cmp_info" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>4 Paws Animal Rescue Inc.</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="3" align="right"><span class="img-border"><img id="change_img" src="https://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/images/organisation/Maple%20(2).jpg" border="0" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="3"><strong>Slogan:</strong> 4 Paws Animal Rescue provides refuge for homeless dogs and cats on the Sunshine Coast in Queensland Australia</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Total Raised:</strong> $59.73</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2"><strong>Description:</strong> 4 Paws Animal Rescue Inc promises a "New Home - New Life" to dogs and cats on the Sunshine Coast in Queensland, Australia. We are a Non Profit Organisation run entirely by volunteers since 2005. 4 Paws takes animals from Council Pounds or those surrendered to us by the public and places them into our wonderful volunteers foster homes. Here they live as part of the family whilst we search for their perfect match forever family. All 4 Paws animals are vet checked, micro chipped, wormed, flea treated and de-sexed prior to being made available for adoption. 4 Paws also has a number of Permanent Residents who are either elderly or have very special needs these animals will remain with our carers forever to ensure they get the very best treatment and care.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Ph: </strong><a href="tel:0411144689">0411144689</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Address :</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>- P O Box 94</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Maroochydore</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Queensland 4558</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="1"><strong>Find Us Online</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/4PawsAnimalRescueInc" target="blank"><span class="img-border"><img class="icons-view" src="https:/