(189, 1, '2017-06-04 19:55:00', '2017-06-04 19:55:00', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span class="img-border"><img id="change_img" src="https://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/images/organisation/Cropped%20AAA%20logo%2090.png" border="0" /></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Slogan:</strong> AAA <strong>Total Raised:</strong> NA <strong>Description:</strong> The Alpha-1 Association of Australia (AAA) is a DGR-registered health charity with the Australia Taxation Office. It is a patient organisation for those in Australia affected by or interested in the genetically inherited condition Alpha-1 Antitrypsin Deficiency. Alpha-1 primarily affects the liver and lungs, but can also have several other organs. Around 1 in 10 people carry the gene, yet awareness is very low. There are many things that can be done, but we need your help to achieve our goals.\r\n\r\n<strong>Ph: </strong><a href="tel:+61 7 3103 3363">+61 7 3103 3363</a> <strong>Address : </strong>2100 GPO Box 2100 Brisbane Queensland 4001 - See more at: https://www.thegivebackcampaign.com/organisations/alpha-1-association-of-australia#sthash.MF1DAdOf.dpuf[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Alpha-1 Association of Australia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'alpha-1-association-of-australia', '', '', '2017-06-04 19:55:00', '2017-06-04 19:55:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/thegivebackcampaign_wp/?post_type=organisations&#038;p=189', 0, 'organisations', '', 0),
